(45329, 1, '2011-11-20 00:01:11', '2011-11-20 07:01:11', '[Brightcove Video]1702533984001[/Brightcove Video]Jana Evans is currently a Human Resource Generalist for Merit Medical in the Salt Lake City, Utah area, which manufactures medical devices all over the globe. After graduating from college, Sister Evans began her career in Human Resources. She started in Technical Recruiting and eventually worked her way to where she is now, an HR Business Generalist. Sister Evans is a member of the Society of Human Resource Management (SHRM) and has received her Professional in Human Resources (PHR) certification. Sister Evans served a mission in South Dakota and is currently serving as the Fellowshipping Activities Co-Chair in a Mid-Singles Branch as well as a pianist for the Spanish Branch Primary in her stake.', 'Janna Evans', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'janna-evans', '', '', '2014-06-30 14:37:04', '2014-06-30 20:37:04', '', 0, 'http://localhost/ldp/htdocs/?p=45329', 0, 'post', '', 0),
