(45356, 1, '2012-02-26 00:01:53', '2012-02-26 07:01:53', '[Brightcove Video]1702613966001[/Brightcove Video]\r\n\r\nGordon Low is the CFO for Valmarc Corporation. The VALMARC Corporation is a Boston-based business technology firm dedicated to developing real-world business solutions to emerging global threats to the profitability and competitiveness of brand product companies and the economies they serve. VALMARCTM technology and tools provide a universal solution for fighting product counterfeiting and gray market diversion, for protecting brands and their intellectual property and for regaining control of mobile marketing and messaging to consumers.\r\n\r\nGordon has over 30 years of business and engineering experience, most recently as a principal at Deloitte.\r\n\r\nGordon is currently President of the Cambridge Massachusetts Stake.', 'Gordon Low', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'gordon-low', '', '', '2014-06-30 14:37:01', '2014-06-30 20:37:01', '', 0, 'http://localhost/ldp/htdocs/?p=45356', 0, 'post', '', 0),
