(45408, 1, '2012-12-16 00:01:39', '2012-12-16 07:01:39', '[Brightcove Video]2137242303001[/Brightcove Video]\r\n\r\nAlan L. Olsen is managing partner at Greenstein Rogoff Olsen &amp; Co., LLP, a leading CPA firm in the San Francisco Bay Area. With more than 25 years of experience in public accounting, he works with some of the most successful\r\nventure capitalists in the world, developing innovative financial strategies for individuals and businesses. His firm was recently recognized by INSIDE Public Accounting as one of the Best Managed CPA firms in the USA. His firm\r\nalso garnered both local and national awards for being one of the "BestPlaces to Work", and "Fastest Growing Companies" in the Bay Area. A nationally recognized speaker, author and consultant, Alan has appeared on\r\nFox News, KPIX and KRON television networks. He has been quoted and published by various media outlets such as CNN Money, Money Magazine, Consumer Reports - Money Advisor, and Money Matters.\r\n\r\nAs chair of the Friends of Scouting Campaign, Alan raised over $1 million and in 2010 he received the Silver Beaver Award from the Boy Scouts of America for distinguished service to youth. He continues to be active in several educational and community foundations. Alan earned a B.S. in Accounting from Brigham Young University and an MBA (Taxation)from California State University in Hayward.He was honored by more than 7,000 Bay Area alumni recognizing his continuous public service advancement and career accomplishments. Recently, he served on President Kim B. Clark''s(Former Dean of the Harvard Business School) Advancement Council at Brigham Young University-Idaho.', 'Alan Olsen', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'alan-olsen', '', '', '2014-06-30 14:36:30', '2014-06-30 20:36:30', '', 0, 'http://localhost/ldp/htdocs/?p=45408', 0, 'post', '', 0),
