(45469, 1, '2013-11-03 00:01:02', '2013-11-03 06:01:02', '[Brightcove Video]2744047239001[/Brightcove Video]\r\n\r\nBorn Brandon Jake Bair on Nov. 24, 1984 in Rexburg, Idaho. Has been married to wife Jordan for  5 years. They have two daughters, Brooklyn (3) and Rylee (1). Parents: Terry and Corina Bair and David and Brenda Miller. Family: Six brothers, one sister. High School (Coach): South Fremont (Cris Tucker) 2003. Red-shirted: 2006 after serving a two year church mission in Jacksonville, Florida where he became fluent in Spanish. College: Oregon, 2006-2010. Graduated June 2010 as an Economics Major, with a Minor in Spanish. NFL: 2011 Made the Kansas City Chiefs active roster. 2012 Was released from the Chiefs following the preseason at which time he was picked up by the Oakland Raiders. He was on the Raiders practice squad until the last game when he was moved to the active roster.', 'Brandon Bair', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'brandon-bair', '', '', '2014-06-30 14:36:03', '2014-06-30 20:36:03', '', 0, 'http://localhost/ldp/htdocs/?p=45469', 0, 'post', '', 0),
